 transition-colors px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-r-bg-soft no-underline\">Contact</a></nav><a href=\"#products\" class=\"text-[13px] font-semibold text-white bg-r-purple hover:bg-r-purple-hover transition-colors px-4 py-2 rounded-lg no-underline\">See our apps</a></header><main><section class=\"relative pt-36 pb-20 px-8 text-center overflow-hidden bg-r-bg\"><div class=\"pointer-events-none absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[800px] h-[420px] opacity-[0.12] blur-[100px]\" style=\"background:radial-gradient(ellipse, #7C3AED 0%, transparent 70%)\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 max-w-[820px] mx-auto\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"r-tag mb-7 mx-auto w-fit\">New · Rasty is live</div><div class=\"mb-6\" style=\"min-height:clamp(56px, 7vw, 96px)\"><h1 class=\"font-black tracking-[-0.03em] leading-[1.08] whitespace-nowrap overflow-hidden\" style=\"font-size:clamp(36px, 5.5vw, 72px)\"><span class=\"inline-block text-r-text\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(60%)\">Apps that </span><span class=\"inline-block text-r-purple\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(60%)\">just work.</span></h1></div><p class=\"text-[16px] leading-[1.8] text-r-muted max-w-[460px] mx-auto mb-10\">We build small apps that handle the stuff you keep putting off. No accounts, no learning curve, no noise.</p><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center gap-3 mb-16\"><a href=\"#products\" class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-[14px] font-semibold text-white bg-r-purple hover:bg-r-purple-hover transition-colors px-6 py-3 rounded-xl no-underline\">Browse our apps<svg width=\"12\" height=\"12\" viewBox=\"0 0 12 12\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M2 6h8M6 2l4 4-4 4\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"#about\" class=\"text-[14px] font-medium text-r-muted hover:text-r-text transition-colors no-underline px-4 py-3\">What is Rasty? →</a></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center gap-16 pt-8 border-t border-r-border\"><div class=\"text-center\"><div class=\"text-[34px] font-black tracking-[-0.03em] text-r-text leading-none mb-1.5\">1</div><div class=\"text-[12px] font-medium text-r-muted\">App live</div></div><div class=\"text-center\"><div class=\"text-[34px] font-black tracking-[-0.03em] text-r-text leading-none mb-1.5\">1.2k+</div><div class=\"text-[12px] font-medium text-r-muted\">Early users</div></div><div class=\"text-center\"><div class=\"text-[34px] font-black tracking-[-0.03em] text-r-text leading-none mb-1.5\">Free</div><div class=\"text-[12px] font-medium text-r-muted\">To start</div></div></div></div></section><div class=\"border-y border-r-border py-3 overflow-hidden select-none bg-r-bg-soft\"><div class=\"marquee-track\"><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-4 px-6 text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-[0.1em] uppercase text-r-muted\">No accounts needed<span class=\"w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-r-purple/30 inline-block\"></span></span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-4 px-6 text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-[0.1em] uppercase text-r-muted\">Actually useful<span class=\"w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-r-purple/30 inline-block\"></span></span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-4 px-6 text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-[0.1em] uppercase text-r-muted\">Built for real life<span class=\"w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-r-purple/30 inline-block\"></span></span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-4 px-6 text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-[0.1em] uppercase text-r-muted\">Free to start<span class=\"w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-r-purple/30 inline-block\"></span></span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-4 px-6 text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-[0.1em] uppercase text-r-muted\">No learning curve<span class=\"w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-r-purple/30 inline-block\"></span></span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-4 px-6 text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-[0.1em] uppercase text-r-muted\">Made by people who use it<span class=\"w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-r-purple/30 inline-block\"></span></span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-4 px-6 text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-[0.1em] uppercase text-r-muted\">No accounts needed<span class=\"w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-r-purple/30 inline-block\"></span></span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-4 px-6 text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-[0.1em] uppercase text-r-muted\">Actually useful<span class=\"w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-r-purple/30 inline-block\"></span></span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-4 px-6 text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-[0.1em] uppercase text-r-muted\">Built for real life<span class=\"w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-r-purple/30 inline-block\"></span></span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-4 px-6 text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-[0.1em] uppercase text-r-muted\">Free to start<span class=\"w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-r-purple/30 inline-block\"></span></span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-4 px-6 text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-[0.1em] uppercase text-r-muted\">No learning curve<span class=\"w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-r-purple/30 inline-block\"></span></span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-4 px-6 text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-[0.1em] uppercase text-r-muted\">Made by people who use it<span class=\"w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-r-purple/30 inline-block\"></span></span></div></div><hr class=\"r-divider\"/><section id=\"products\" class=\"max-w-[1100px] mx-auto px-8 py-24\"><div class=\"text-center mb-16\" style=\"opacity:0;filter:blur(4px);transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"r-tag mb-5 mx-auto w-fit\">Products</div><h2 class=\"font-black text-r-text tracking-[-0.03em] leading-[1.1] mb-4\" style=\"font-size:clamp(32px, 4.5vw, 54px)\">Apps we&#x27;ve built</h2><p class=\"text-[15px] text-r-muted max-w-[380px] mx-auto leading-[1.7]\">Each one does one thing. And does it well.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 max-md:grid-cols-1\"><a href=\"https://dodo.rasty.uk\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"group relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden p-8 flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[360px] no-underline border border-r-purple-light bg-r-purple-faint hover:bg-r-purple-light transition-colors duration-300\" style=\"opacity:0;filter:blur(4px);transform:translateY(24px)\"><div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-8\"><div class=\"w-11 h-11 rounded-xl bg-white border border-r-purple-light flex items-center justify-center text-xl shadow-sm\">🐦</div><span class=\"text-[11px] font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-700 border border-emerald-200\">Live</span></div><div class=\"text-[10px] font-bold tracking-[0.12em] uppercase text-r-purple/50 mb-2\">Free · iOS &amp; Android</div><h3 class=\"text-[30px] font-black text-r-text tracking-[-0.03em] mb-3\">Dodo</h3><p class=\"text-[14px] font-semibold text-r-text mb-2\">Stop forgetting the important stuff.</p><p class=\"text-[14px] leading-[1.72] text-r-muted max-w-[300px]\">Dodo tracks the things that keep slipping — doctor visits, bill splits, ID renewals, lease dates. Tap what applies to your life. It handles the rest.</p></div><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between pt-6 border-t border-r-purple-light mt-6\"><span class=\"text-[13px] font-semibold text-r-purple\">Try Dodo free</span><svg width=\"11\" height=\"11\" viewBox=\"0 0 12 12\" fill=\"none\" class=\"text-r-purple group-hover:translate-x-0.5 group-hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-transform\"><path d=\"M2 10L10 2M10 2H4M10 2v6\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path></svg></div></a><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-4\"><div class=\"rounded-2xl p-7 border border-r-border bg-r-bg-soft flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[168px]\" style=\"opacity:0;filter:blur(4px);transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-4\"><div><div class=\"text-[10px] font-bold tracking-[0.12em] uppercase text-r-muted mb-2\">In the pipeline</div><h3 class=\"text-[20px] font-black text-r-text tracking-[-0.02em] mb-1.5\">More apps coming</h3><p class=\"text-[13px] text-r-muted leading-[1.65]\">One at a time. Done right.</p></div><span class=\"text-[11px] font-semibold px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-white text-r-muted border border-r-border shrink-0\">Soon</span></div></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl p-7 border border-r-border bg-white flex-1 min-h-[172px]\" style=\"opacity:0;filter:blur(4px);transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"text-[10px] font-bold tracking-[0.12em] uppercase text-r-muted mb-5\">How we build</div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3.5\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><span class=\"text-[10px] font-bold text-r-muted/40 tabular-nums w-4 shrink-0\">0<!-- -->1</span><span class=\"text-[13px] font-semibold text-r-text\">Free to try</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><span class=\"text-[10px] font-bold text-r-muted/40 tabular-nums w-4 shrink-0\">0<!-- -->2</span><span class=\"text-[13px] font-semibold text-r-text\">No setup required</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><span class=\"text-[10px] font-bold text-r-muted/40 tabular-nums w-4 shrink-0\">0<!-- -->3</span><span class=\"text-[13px] font-semibold text-r-text\">Works in the background</span></div></div></div></div></div></section><hr class=\"r-divider\"/><section id=\"about\" class=\"bg-r-bg-soft py-24 px-8\"><div class=\"max-w-[1100px] mx-auto\"><div class=\"text-center mb-16\" style=\"opacity:0;filter:blur(4px);transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"r-tag mb-5 mx-auto w-fit\">About</div><h2 class=\"font-black text-r-text tracking-[-0.03em] leading-[1.1] mb-4\" style=\"font-size:clamp(28px, 4vw, 48px)\">Built by people who got tired<br/>of bad software.</h2><p class=\"text-[15px] text-r-muted max-w-[440px] mx-auto leading-[1.75]\">Rasty is a small independent studio. We build apps for ourselves first — if we wouldn&#x27;t use it daily, we don&#x27;t ship it.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 max-md:grid-cols-1\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl p-7 border border-r-border hover:border-r-purple-light hover:shadow-sm transition-all duration-200\" style=\"opacity:0;filter:blur(4px);transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"text-[11px] font-bold tracking-[0.1em] text-r-muted/40 mb-5\">01</div><h3 class=\"text-[15px] font-bold text-r-text mb-3 tracking-[-0.01em]\">One app, one job</h3><p class=\"text-[13px] leading-[1.72] text-r-muted\">We don&#x27;t add features for the sake of it. Every tap has a reason.</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl p-7 border border-r-border hover:border-r-purple-light hover:shadow-sm transition-all duration-200\" style=\"opacity:0;filter:blur(4px);transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"text-[11px] font-bold tracking-[0.1em] text-r-muted/40 mb-5\">02</div><h3 class=\"text-[15px] font-bold text-r-text mb-3 tracking-[-0.01em]\">No babysitting</h3><p class=\"text-[13px] leading-[1.72] text-r-muted\">You shouldn&#x27;t need to check an app for it to work. Ours run quietly until you actually need them.</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl p-7 border border-r-border hover:border-r-purple-light hover:shadow-sm transition-all duration-200\" style=\"opacity:0;filter:blur(4px);transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"text-[11px] font-bold tracking-[0.1em] text-r-muted/40 mb-5\">03</div><h3 class=\"text-[15px] font-bold text-r-text mb-3 tracking-[-0.01em]\">Free first</h3><p class=\"text-[13px] leading-[1.72] text-r-muted\">Every Rasty app is free to start. No credit card, no trial countdown, no pressure.</p></div></div></div></section><hr class=\"r-divider\"/><section class=\"px-8 py-24 bg-r-bg\"><div class=\"max-w-[1100px] mx-auto\"><div class=\"text-center mb-16\" style=\"opacity:0;filter:blur(4px);transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"r-tag mb-5 mx-auto w-fit\">What&#x27;s next</div><h2 class=\"font-black text-r-text tracking-[-0.03em] leading-[1.1] mb-4\" style=\"font-size:clamp(28px, 4vw, 48px)\">What we&#x27;re working on</h2><p class=\"text-[15px] text-r-muted max-w-[400px] mx-auto leading-[1.75]\">Early ideas. No promises. But here&#x27;s where we&#x27;re headed.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 max-md:grid-cols-1\"><div class=\"rounded-2xl p-7 border border-r-border bg-white hover:shadow-sm transition-all duration-200 flex flex-col gap-5 relative overflow-hidden\" style=\"opacity:0;filter:blur(4px);transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none transition-opacity duration-300\" style=\"opacity:0;background:radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.12) 0%, transparent 65%)\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"r-tag\">Finance</span><span class=\"text-[11px] font-semibold text-r-muted\">Q3 2026</span></div><div class=\"relative z-10\"><h3 class=\"text-[18px] font-black text-r-muted/60 tracking-[-0.02em] mb-3 italic\">Untitled</h3><p class=\"text-[14px] leading-[1.72] text-r-text font-medium\">See every subscription you&#x27;re paying for. Cancel what you forgot about.</p></div><div class=\"relative z-10 mt-auto pt-4 border-t border-r-border\"><span class=\"text-[12px] font-medium text-r-muted/40\">Details TBA</span></div></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl p-7 border border-r-border bg-white hover:shadow-sm transition-all duration-200 flex flex-col gap-5 relative overflow-hidden\" style=\"opacity:0;filter:blur(4px);transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none transition-opacity duration-300\" style=\"opacity:0;background:radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, rgba(244, 63, 94, 0.12) 0%, transparent 65%)\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"r-tag\">Health</span><span class=\"text-[11px] font-semibold text-r-muted\">Q4 2026</span></div><div class=\"relative z-10\"><h3 class=\"text-[18px] font-black text-r-muted/60 tracking-[-0.02em] mb-3 italic\">Untitled</h3><p class=\"text-[14px] leading-[1.72] text-r-text font-medium\">Know what&#x27;s worth tracking. Ignore the rest.</p></div><div class=\"relative z-10 mt-auto pt-4 border-t border-r-border\"><span class=\"text-[12px] font-medium text-r-muted/40\">Details TBA</span></div></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl p-7 border border-r-border bg-white hover:shadow-sm transition-all duration-200 flex flex-col gap-5 relative overflow-hidden\" style=\"opacity:0;filter:blur(4px);transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none transition-opacity duration-300\" style=\"opacity:0;background:radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.12) 0%, transparent 65%)\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"r-tag\">Mobile IDE</span><span class=\"text-[11px] font-semibold text-r-muted\">Q1 2027</span></div><div class=\"relative z-10\"><h3 class=\"text-[18px] font-black text-r-muted/60 tracking-[-0.02em] mb-3 italic\">Untitled</h3><p class=\"text-[14px] leading-[1.72] text-r-text font-medium\">Code on your phone like you&#x27;re at a desk. Custom keyboard, trackpad strip, on-device Python and JS. No compromises.</p></div><div class=\"relative z-10 mt-auto pt-4 border-t border-r-border\"><span class=\"text-[12px] font-medium text-r-muted/40\">Details TBA</span></div></div></div></div></section></main><footer class=\"border-t border-r-border bg-r-bg-soft\"><div class=\"max-w-[1100px] mx-auto px-8\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between py-10 gap-8 max-md:flex-col max-md:items-start\"><div><a href=\"/\" class=\"text-[20px] font-black text-r-text no-underline tracking-tight block mb-1.5\">Rasty</a><p class=\"text-[13px] text-r-muted max-w-[200px] leading-[1.6]\">Small apps. Big difference.</p></div><nav class=\"flex items-center gap-1 flex-wrap\"><a href=\"#products\" class=\"text-[13px] font-medium text-r-muted hover:text-r-text transition-colors px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-white no-underline\">Products</a><a href=\"#about\" c